{"title_page": "Sosuke Shibata", "text_new": "{{short description|Japanese footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Sosuke Shibata<br/>\u67f4\u7530 \u58ee\u4ecb\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Sosuke Shibata\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|2001|5|26}}\n|birth_place=[[Nagasaki Prefecture|Nagasaki]], Japan\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.68}}\n|position=[[Midfielder]]\n|currentclub=[[Shonan Bellmare]]\n|clubnumber=30\n|youthyears1=|youthclubs1=[[Shonan Bellmare]]\n|years1=2018\u2013|clubs1=[[Shonan Bellmare]]|caps1=0|goals1=0\n|totalcaps=|totalgoals=\n|nationalyears1=|nationalteam1=|nationalcaps1=|nationalgoals1=\n|manageryears1=|managerclubs1=\n|medaltemplates=\n{{Medal|Team|[[Shonan Bellmare]]}}\n{{Medal|W|[[J.League Cup]]|[[2018 J.League Cup|2018]]}}\n|club-update= 14 January 2019\n|nationalteam-update=\n}}\n{{Nihongo|'''Sosuke Shibata'''|\u67f4\u7530 \u58ee\u4ecb|Shibata S\u014dsuke|born May 26, 2001}} is a [[Japan]]ese [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>{{J.League player}}</ref>\n\n==Playing career==\nShibata was born in [[Nagasaki Prefecture]] on May 26, 2001. He joined [[J1 League]] club [[Shonan Bellmare]] from youth team in 2018.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{J.League player}}\n\n{{Shonan Bellmare squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Shibata, Sosuke}}\n[[Category:2001 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Nagasaki Prefecture]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J1 League players]]\n[[Category:Shonan Bellmare players]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-midfielder-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Sosuke Shibata<br/>\u67f4\u7530 \u58ee\u4ecb\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Sosuke Shibata\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|2001|5|26}}\n|birth_place=[[Nagasaki Prefecture|Nagasaki]], Japan\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.68}}\n|position=[[Midfielder]]\n|